  "text": "Clinical assessments were done based on the Japan Orthopaedic Association (JOA) score for CSM patients. Both upper-and lower-extremity functions were evaluated in this study. All patients were clinically evaluated before the operation and re-evaluated at 12 weeks postoperatively. The surgical outcome was represented by the JOA score recovery rate as calculated by the formula of Hirabayashi et al [CITATION_1] .",
